THIS LETTER-WRITING'S
A MENACE. I MEAN,
YOU WRITE THEM.
SOME POOR WRETCH HAS TO
READ THEM. HE WRITES
YOU BACK AGAIN.
YOU HAVE TO ANSWER IT.
I MEAN, WHERE ARE YOU?
I MEAN,
THE WHOLE THING'S
INTERMINABLE.
IT DOESN'T MEAN
ANYTHING.
NATASHA,
WILL YOU MARRY ME?
I'M GOING TO!
I MEAN NOW.
PAUL--
LISTEN, DARLING.
IT DOESN'T HELP
THE DEAD ANY
TO STOP LIVING
JUST BECAUSE
THEY'RE GONE.
YOU DON'T KNOW HOW I FEEL
ABOUT THESE THINGS.
I KNOW, SWEETHEART.
I SUPPOSE RELIGION'S
A WONDERFUL THING.
