I'VE HAD
THE SAME FEELING
BRUSHING
AGAINST SOMETHING
ON A DARK NIGHT.
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT HE'S AFTER,
BUT I GET A SORT
OF FEELING OF A MAN
WAITING HIS CHANCE.
PAUL!
